{"tid":1077770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【三隻小豬】港人疑衝入闡 被放上內地社交平台公開處刑","createTime":"2019-03-25T22:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T01:25:38.000Z","uid":70867,"like":35,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a2087f4d22fef0908434780d13d9f3736c6622b6","tid":1077770,"uid":70867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T22:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k799HGv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk799HGv.png&h=16ca2bf4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ingsumw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fingsumw.png&h=de6e1b92&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0wJq0tc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0wJq0tc.png&h=3a52e7b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時無聊會睇下小紅書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家勿屌<br />\n<br />\n不過睇到呢個post實在有感而發<br />\n講真 香港人不嬲少打尖<br />\n見到大陸人嘅情況下例外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為都預左 我地唔打就比佢地打<br />\n所以真係唔讓得<br />\n我覺得呢個大陸人係爭唔到位<br />\n老羞成怒就擺人上黎<br />\n仲要開曬人地樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果當然引左一班人留言話香港乜乜柒柒<br />\n不過其實好多留言係大陸人自己都覺得大陸先多人打尖，反而香港少<br />\n事實嘅野唔到佢地唔認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過 三隻小豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地今次真係做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地公開處刑你<br />\n我地公開表揚你"},{"pid":"89563407153a59e9e8b91669c797a944d450633f","tid":1077770,"uid":128761,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T22:56:52.000Z","msg":"中間打扮係中國人黎架下嘛"},{"pid":"7665972a4ded579177ec9143be12f669e2cd5e42","tid":1077770,"uid":152123,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"